data.description: *** FHA Assumable loan!  Welcome home! This  desired rambler floor plan home was built in 2020 with plenty of upgrades through out. The open concept for kitchen, dinning, and living room is perfect for convenient living and entertainment purposes. This home comes fully landscaped front and back. Solar was recently installed on roof with  EV charger in the spacious & extended 2 car garage.  There are 2 vanities in both of the 2 full bathrooms. Granite countertops in all the bathrooms and kitchen. Incredible mountain views from this home.  Don't under estimate the quick access to all retail convenience nearby. Come tour today!  Square footage figures are provided as a courtesy estimate only.  Buyer is advised to obtain an independent measurement.
